an>(Ca2+ and Mg2+ free) to 240 ml, adjust to <\/span><a href=\"#\" style = \"text-decoration:underline;color:blue;cursor:pointer;\"><span style = \":;\"> <\/span><\/a><span> with NaOH or HCl, bring to 250 ml with PBS.<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\">The substances are in the closet 1 and in refrigerator 1 (Room TSO8), weigh the substances with Gibertini balance (Room TSO8).<\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-weight:bold;\">Filter  buffer 1 using sterile syringe and filter.<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\">Sterile filters and syringes are in closet 1 (Room PSO3).<\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span>Storage:<\/span><a href=\"#\" style = \"text-decoration:underline;color:blue;cursor:pointer;\"><span style = \":;\"> <\/span><\/a><span> refrigerator 2 - (Room PSO3).<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-weight:bold;\">Buffer 2<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-weight:bold;\">RPMI\/FBS 1% (v\/v)<\/span><span>: prepare with sterile RPMI and FBS (Fetal Bovine Serum). Both can be found in refrigerator 2 - (Room PSO3).<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span>Prepare 50 ml of RPMI\/FBS by adding <\/span><a href=\"#\" style = \"text-decoration:underline;color:blue;cursor:pointer;\"><span style = \":;\"> <\/span><\/a><span> of FBS to <\/span><a href=\"#\" style = \"text-decoration:underline;color:blue;cursor:pointer;\"><span style = \":;\"> <\/span><\/a><span> of RPMI, work under a laminar flow hood (Room PSO3).<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span>Storage: <\/span><a href=\"#\" style = \"text-decoration:underline;color:blue;cursor:pointer;\"><span style = \":;\"> <\/span><\/a><span> refrigerator 2 - (Room PSO3).<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-weight:bold;\">BSA: <\/span><span>catalog number A2153\u00a0, Sigma, Italy<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-weight:bold;\">RPMI:<\/span><span> catalog number ECM0495L, Euroclone, Italy.<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-weight:bold;\">FBS:<\/span><span> catalog number ECS0180L, Euroclone, Italy.<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-weight:bold;\">EDTA<\/span><span>: catalog number ED2SS, Sigma, Italy<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-weight:bold;\">Prymo siringe filter<\/span><span>: catalog number EPSPE2230 Euroclone, Italy.<\/span><\/div><\/div>","materials":[],"description":null,"changed_on":1590589297}